
Current Architecture

src/                              scripts/ (pygpen reference)
├── entities/                     ├── pygpen/
│   ├── player.py                ├── state.py
│   ├── blue.py                  ├── physics_entity.py
│   └── projectiles.py           ├── tilemap.py
├── systems/                      ├── effects.py
│   ├── debug.py                 └── ... (many specialized modules)
│   └── projectile_manager.py
└── main.py

Future Architecture

memento/
├── engine/                    # Core engine functionality
│   ├── window.py             # Display management
│   ├── renderer.py           # Drawing system
│   ├── asset_manager.py      # Resource loading/caching
│   └── input_handler.py      # Input management
│
├── world/                    # World management
│   ├── chunk_manager.py      # Chunk-based loading
│   ├── quadtree.py          # Spatial partitioning
│   └── camera.py            # View culling/rendering
│
├── entities/                 # Game objects
│   ├── base/
│   │   ├── entity.py        # Base entity class
│   │   └── physics_entity.py # Physics-enabled base
│   ├── player/
│   │   ├── player.py        # Player logic
│   │   └── states.py        # Player states
│   └── enemies/
│       └── blue.py          # Blue enemy
│
├── systems/                  # Game systems
│   ├── physics/
│   │   ├── collision.py     # Collision detection
│   │   └── movement.py      # Movement handling
│   ├── combat/
│   │   ├── projectile.py    # Projectile management
│   │   └── damage.py        # Damage handling
│   └── debug/
│       ├── logger.py        # Logging system
│       └── visualizer.py    # Debug visualization
│
├── ui/                      # User interface
│   ├── hud.py              # Heads-up display
│   ├── menus.py            # Menu system
│   └── debug_overlay.py    # Debug information
│
└── game.py                 # Main entry point